<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2010-07-08.S3W-34736.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80312" speakername="George Foulkes (Lothians) (Lab)" spid="S3W-34736" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-10/wa0708.htm#3">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive what consideration has been given to the need to improve the central collection of data in relation to (a) health services and (b) education to inform planning decisions.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2010-07-08.S3W-34736.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80396" speakername="Nicola Sturgeon" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-10/wa0708.htm#3">

